				<h2>Intermountain Standards</h2>
				<p>The Enterprise Architecture Review Board committee is responsible for the oversight of Information Systems standards across the enterprise. The
					committee relies on several teams for the analysis and review of all standards, including but not limited to the Enterprise Solution Architecture (ESA)
					team, the Information Systems Security & Advocacy (ISSA) team and the various IS Operations teams.</p>
			</div>

