						<dt>Enterprise Architecture Review Board (EARB)</dt>
						<dd>Committee made up of representatives from all parts of the enterprise. They meet as a review board on the fourth Tuesday of every month. The
							board reviews proposals for standardization, as well as any exceptions to standards.</dd>
						<dt>IDEA</dt>
						<dd>Committee to review all software standards, including development systems.</dd>
